    <h1>Jira Cloud → Th1ngs Migration</h1>
    <p class="doc-lead" style="font-size:1.03rem; color:var(--muted); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom:1.5rem; margin-bottom:2rem;">
      Gap analysis &amp; technical requirements for a full migration of a Jira Cloud instance into Th1ngs.
    </p>

    <blockquote>
      Scope: Full migration of a Jira Cloud instance (projects, issues, users, workflows) into a running Th1ngs deployment.
    </blockquote>

