    <h2 id="data-transform">6. Data Transformation Reference</h2>

    <h3>6.1 Custom Field Type Mapping</h3>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Jira Field Schema Type</th><th>Th1ngs Field Type</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><code>string</code></td><td><code>TEXT</code> → FieldStringValue</td><td>Truncate at 100 chars; overflow to BLOB.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>number</code></td><td><code>NUMBER</code> → FieldNumberValue</td><td>Double.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>date</code>, <code>datetime</code></td><td><code>DATE</code> → FieldDateValue</td><td>Normalize to UTC.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>array</code> (of strings/options)</td><td><code>MULTI</code> → FieldMultiValue + FieldOption</td><td>Create FieldOption rows for each value.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>option</code> (single select)</td><td><code>TEXT</code> → FieldStringValue</td><td>Use option label.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>user</code></td><td><code>TEXT</code> → store accountId</td><td>No native user-type field in Th1ngs.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>textarea</code> / wiki markup</td><td><code>BLOB</code> → FieldBlobValue</td><td>Strip Jira Wiki markup or convert to plain text.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>url</code></td><td><code>TEXT</code> → FieldStringValue</td><td></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>labels</code></td><td>Native THING_LABEL join (CH-05)</td><td></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>priority</code></td><td>Native THI_PRIORITY column (CH-02)</td><td></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>sprint</code></td><td>THI_MILESTONE_ID FK (CH-02)</td><td></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>story_points</code></td><td>NUMBER field, FLD_KEY = <code>story_points</code></td><td></td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>6.2 Issue Link Type Mapping</h3>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Jira Link Type</th><th>TRE_TYPE Code</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Blocks</td><td>3</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Duplicates</td><td>4</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Relates to</td><td>5</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Clones</td><td>6</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Causes</td><td>7</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Epic-Link (child of epic)</td><td>1 (parent-of)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sub-task</td><td>2 (subtask)</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>6.3 Jira Status Category Mapping</h3>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Jira Status Category</th><th>Th1ngs State Category</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><code>new</code> (To Do)</td><td><code>todo</code> (STA_CATEGORY = 1)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>indeterminate</code> (In Progress)</td><td><code>in_progress</code> (STA_CATEGORY = 2)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>done</code></td><td><code>done</code> (STA_CATEGORY = 3)</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>6.4 User Mapping</h3>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Jira User Field</th><th>Th1ngs Field</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><code>accountId</code></td><td>ACCOUNTID (max 40 chars)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>displayName</code></td><td>fullName</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>emailAddress</code></td><td>email</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>active</code></td><td>enabled</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p>Imported users receive a <strong>random locked password</strong> (bcrypt hash of UUID). They must reset via the Th1ngs password-reset flow or an admin sets their credentials.</p>

    <h3>6.5 Rich Text / Description Conversion</h3>
    <p>Jira Cloud uses <strong>Atlassian Document Format (ADF)</strong> for issue descriptions and comments. Th1ngs stores plain text / basic HTML.</p>
    <p><strong>Required:</strong> Integrate a small ADF-to-HTML converter. Minimum viable: strip ADF to plain text using a recursive JSON walker.</p>

    <hr>

    <h2 id="migration-sequence">7. Migration Sequence</h2>
    <p>Execute steps in this order to preserve referential integrity:</p>
    <pre><code>1. Pre-flight checks
   ├── Validate Jira API token (GET /rest/api/3/myself)
   ├── Verify target Site exists in Th1ngs
   └── Confirm all CH-01…CH-15 changes are deployed

2. Seed global data
   ├── Insert THING_RELATION_TYPE rows (CH-06)
   └── Insert target PrioritySchema rows

3. Per-project import loop
   ├── 3a.  Import Users (idempotent by ACCOUNTID)
   ├── 3b.  Import Groups and Group Memberships
   ├── 3c.  Create Box (project → box, skip if BOX_KEY exists)
   ├── 3d.  Create / reuse ThingTypeSchema for the Box
   ├── 3e.  Create ThingTypes (issue types)
   ├── 3f.  Generate Workflow YAML + insert Workflow + WorkflowTransition rows
   ├── 3g.  Link WorkflowThingTypeSchema to Box
   ├── 3h.  Create Custom Field definitions (Field rows)
   ├── 3i.  Create BoxAccessUser/Group records (project members/roles)
   ├── 3j.  Create BoxMilestone rows (sprints)
   ├── 3k.  Create BoxRelease rows (fix versions)
   ├── 3l.  Import Issues (Things) — first pass, no links
   ├── 3m.  Import Issue Links (ThingRelation rows)
   ├── 3n.  Import Epic/Parent relations (THI_PARENT_ID)
   ├── 3o.  Import Comments (ThingComment)
   ├── 3p.  Import Worklogs (ThingWorklog) if enabled
   ├── 3q.  Import Attachments (ThingAttachment + GCS upload) if enabled
   ├── 3r.  Import Watchers (ThingWatcher) if enabled
   └── 3s.  Import Labels and THING_LABEL rows

4. Post-import validation
   ├── Count: Jira issues vs imported Things per project
   ├── Verify all state values exist in workflow
   ├── Log unresolved user references
   └── Output import summary report</code></pre>

    <hr>

    <h2 id="risks">8. Risk Register</h2>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>ID</th><th>Risk</th><th>Likelihood</th><th>Impact</th><th>Mitigation</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>R-01</td><td>Jira API rate limits (10 req/s on Cloud free tier)</td><td>High</td><td>Medium</td><td>Implement exponential backoff + <code>Retry-After</code> header handling.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>R-02</td><td>ADF description conversion loses formatting</td><td>High</td><td>Low</td><td>Store raw ADF JSON in a <code>FieldBlobValue</code> as fallback.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>R-03</td><td>BOX_KEY collision (Jira project key &gt; 10 chars)</td><td>Medium</td><td>High</td><td>Truncate + append numeric suffix; log collisions for manual review.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>R-04</td><td>User email not available (Jira privacy settings)</td><td>Medium</td><td>Medium</td><td>Use <code>accountId</code> as username; flag for admin review post-import.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>R-05</td><td>Jira attachments exceed GCS quota</td><td>Low</td><td>High</td><td>Add <code>importAttachments: false</code> dry-run option; report total attachment size before importing.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>R-06</td><td>Custom workflow with &gt;50 statuses</td><td>Low</td><td>Medium</td><td>YAML generation must handle large status sets; test WorkflowLoader parsing.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>R-07</td><td>Jira issue key format (&gt;10 char project key)</td><td>Medium</td><td>Low</td><td>Store original Jira key in a <code>FieldStringValue</code> (FLD_KEY=<code>jira_issue_key</code>).</td></tr>
        <tr><td>R-08</td><td>Data volume: &gt;100k issues</td><td>Medium</td><td>High</td><td>Paginate Jira API calls (max 100/page); batch-insert using <code>saveAll()</code> per 500 records.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>R-09</td><td>Multi-project user overlap (same user in two projects)</td><td>High</td><td>Low</td><td>Idempotent by ACCOUNTID logic prevents duplicates.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>R-10</td><td>Jira sub-tasks imported before parent issues</td><td>Medium</td><td>High</td><td>Import all issues first (step 3l) before resolving parent links (step 3n).</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

